OL,7,FBusinesses along a flooded road in say
OL,8,Fthey are losing customers, with some
OL,9,Flikening the situation to navigating a
OL,10,Fcanal rather than a road.
OL,12,FAmong the affected on Chemical Lane,
OL,13,Fin Longport, is the waste management
OL,14,Fcompany Belford Bros, which says it
OL,15,Fhas experienced substantial trade
OL,16,Flosses.JThe floodwaters, exceeding
OL,17,Fthree feet in certain areas, have
OL,18,Fforced motorists to abandon their
OL,19,Fvehicles because of the deluge.
