OL,7,FBusiness owner Sam Belford said: "This
OL,8,Fflooding is horrendous and it has been
OL,9,Fan ongoing issue for years. Luckily, I
OL,10,Fwork from the head office in Ball
OL,11,FGreen but the reclamation yard is run
OL,12,Ffrom exactly where the flooding is.
OL,13,F"It's right outside the yard so people
OL,14,Fare not coming because it's so badly
OL,15,Fflooded so we're losing business. My
OL,16,Fphone has been like a hot cake with
OL,17,Fpeople asking if they can come in, but
OL,18,Fthe water is so deep that it's a risk
OL,19,Fto their cars.J"We've had people
OL,20,Ftrying to drive through the flood and
OL,21,Ftheir car has cut out so they've had
OL,22,Fto get out and push - and the water
OL,23,Fcomes up to their knees.
