OL,8,Fup driving through it but luckily it
OL,9,Fwas near Moores Metals so they had to
OL,10,Ftake it there.
OL,12,F"I run 18-tonne lorries and I have a
OL,13,F10-tonne lorry that can just about
OL,14,Fmanage to drive through it because
OL,15,Fotherwise it would be bringing my
OL,16,Fbusiness to an absolute halt.
