OL,7,F"Staffordshire County Council is
OL,8,Fsaying it's not an emergency - how
OL,9,Fdoes that not warrant an emergency?
OL,10,F"It only takes a drizzle of rain and
OL,11,Fthe water pours out. I can't
OL,12,Funderstand where it even comes from.
OL,13,FNetwork Rail and Severn Trent don't
OL,14,Fwant to know about it because a
OL,15,Fdrainage pipe has collapsed underneath
OL,16,Fthe railway and it'll be a massive job
OL,17,Fto sort it that will lose them money."
