OL,7,FNetwork Rail is checking its land
OL,8,Ffollowing this week's issues.JA
OL,9,FNetwork Rail spokesman said: "We are
OL,10,Faware of the flooding issues on
OL,11,FChemical Lane and we've been working
OL,12,Fwith the local authority to identify
OL,13,Fthe issue.
OL,15,F"We have checked the drainage under
OL,16,Fthe railway and there are no issues.
OL,17,FHowever the local stream owned by a
OL,18,Fthird party is blocked and can back up
OL,19,Fonto the road.
