OL,7,F"We will continue to work with the
OL,8,Fcouncil to see how we can help clear
OL,9,Fthe road for local residents and
OL,10,Fbusinesses as soon as possible."
OL,11,FStaffordshire County Council - which
OL,12,Fis responsible for the road - is
OL,13,Fblaming the issue on a 'temporary pump
OL,14,Fsystem'.
OL,16,FCouncillor David Williams, cabinet
OL,17,Fmember for highways, said: "Our
OL,18,Fhighways crews have been made aware of
OL,19,Fan issue with the temporary pump
OL,20,Fsystem used to pump excess water away
OL,21,Ffrom the road.
